          <title>
            <string language="sl">Procesiranje informacij na strojnem nivoju</string>
            <string language="en">Processing on machine-level</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Verarbeitung auf Maschine-Stufe</string>

            <string language="x-mt-pt">Processar no máquina-nível</string>

          <language>sl</language>
          <description>
            <string language="sl">Poglavje o procesiranje informacij na strojnem nivoju v sklopu e-gradiva za računalništvo in informatiko. Vsebina poglavja: arhitektura računalnika, registri, naslavlanje, sklad, pasti, prekinitve.</string>
            <string language="en">Chapter about processing on machine-level, part of e-materials for computer science and informatics. Chapter contents: computer architecture, registers, indexing, stack, traps, interrupts.</string>
          </description>

Maschine-Stufe, Teil Ematerialien für Informatik und Informatik. 
Kapitelinhalt: Computerarchitektur, Register, 
Index-Bewegung, Stapel, Fallen, unterbricht.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Chapitre au sujet du traitement sur le 
machine-niveau, partie d'e-matériels pour l'informatique et 
informatique. Contenu de chapitre : l'architecture 
d'ordinateur, registres, indexation, pile, pièges, s'interrompt.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Capítulo sobre processar no máquina-nível,

Índices do capítulo: a arquitetura de computador, 
registos, indexing, pilha, armadilhas, interrompe.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Capitolo circa elaborare sul macchina-livello 
facente parte i e-materiali per informatica ed informatica. 
Soddisfare di capitolo: l'architettura di calcolatore, i 
registri, il indexing, la pila, prese, interrompe.</string>
          </description>
          <description>

μέρος των ε-υλικών για την πληροφορική και την πληροφορική.

κατάλογοι, ευρετηρίαση, στοίβα, παγιδεύει, διακόπτει.</string>
          </description>

Contenido del capítulo: la configuración de ordenador, 
registros, indexación de direcciones, pila, desvíos, interrumpe.</string>
